val tweet_friends = sqlContext.sql("SELECT user.friends_count FROM tweets")

%sql

select  user.friends_count as fc, count(*) as tweet_count
FROM tweets
where user.friends_count < 5000
group by user.friends_count

select count(*) from tweets where user.friends_count > ${maxFriends=1000}

select  
user.friends_count as fc, 
count(id) as tweet_count 
FROM tweets 
group by user.friends_count 
having count(id) < 50
